Author: earlgreybaby
Text: I dont think it will become a habit because I dont let myself binge (the idea of eating even if throwing up scares me) thank you for the response :)

Author: fishonthesun
Text: The achy is normal. I'm basically bulimic at this point, and it aches every time. Please dont let it become a habit )-: I've purged less than 20 times and my gums are super sensitive and bleed so easily already. It's a terrible habit to get into, it takes up so much time and money, and the symptoms just get worse and worse
